  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Safety and Efficacy of GB-0998 in Unexplained Primary Recurrent Miscarriage</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Double-blinded Study With GB-0998 for Unexplained Primary Recurrent Miscarriage</official_title>
  <sponsors>
