  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To estimate the safety and efficacy of intravenous immunoglobulin therapy using GB-0998 in
      women with four or more miscarriages by carrying out randomized, placebo-controlled,
      double-blinded study．
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
